<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Taro.</font>

2
00:00:06,130 --> 00:00:07,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nio.</font>

3
00:00:08,020 --> 00:00:09,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hajime.</font>

4
00:00:10,240 --> 00:00:11,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You brats...</font>

5
00:00:13,400 --> 00:00:16,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...grew into fine young men 
while I wasn't looking.</font>

6
00:00:18,150 --> 00:00:21,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I remember someone 
called you a trio of wolves.</font>

7
00:00:21,500 --> 00:00:24,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, now you truly live up to the name.</font>

8
00:00:25,370 --> 00:00:26,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um...</font>

9
00:00:26,410 --> 00:00:27,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Taro.</font>

10
00:00:28,780 --> 00:00:31,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't need to feel 
indebted to me anymore.</font>

11
00:00:36,580 --> 00:00:40,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've done your loyal duty, 
and done it well.</font>

12
00:00:41,260 --> 00:00:42,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Serizawa-sensei.</font>

13
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:45,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nio.</font>

14
00:00:45,910 --> 00:00:51,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought you were an odd, 
uppity little novice at first, but now?</font>

15
00:00:52,240 --> 00:00:55,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You want to protect the weak,
 and get stronger.</font>

16
00:00:55,860 --> 00:00:58,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's the root of it.</font>

17
00:00:59,040 --> 00:01:04,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you know, if you insist on ideals, 
life will only get harder.</font>

18
00:01:04,640 --> 00:01:08,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Miburo aren't what 
you want us to be anymore.</font>

19
00:01:08,850 --> 00:01:10,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know you see that.</font>

20
00:01:13,470 --> 00:01:14,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hajime.</font>

21
00:01:15,600 --> 00:01:19,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have skill, 
but don't follow in my footsteps.</font>

22
00:01:20,280 --> 00:01:23,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't let the ghost 
of the samurai trap you.</font>

23
00:01:24,920 --> 00:01:29,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're all free now! 
Live however you like!</font>

