<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia">{\an8}<b><font size="60"><font color="#0c49ea">Blue Miburo</font></font></b></font></font>

42
00:03:17,300 --> 00:03:19,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Serizawa-san, if you would.</font>

43
00:03:19,550 --> 00:03:20,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure.</font>

44
00:03:21,440 --> 00:03:25,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My dear ronin of Mibu! 
You've served well, day in and day out.</font>

45
00:03:25,660 --> 00:03:29,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Shogunate has granted us 
a special reward.</font>

46
00:03:29,920 --> 00:03:31,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Drink the night away.</font>

47
00:03:31,940 --> 00:03:34,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Get to know" any woman 
who strikes your fancy.</font>

48
00:03:34,980 --> 00:03:37,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry about money.</font>

49
00:03:37,230 --> 00:03:40,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just enjoy yourselves in style! Cheers!</font>

50
00:03:41,170 --> 00:03:43,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Drink up!</font>

51
00:03:49,110 --> 00:03:51,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong, Sir Kondo?</font>

52
00:03:51,060 --> 00:03:53,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A leader's gotta cut a fine figure.</font>

53
00:03:53,610 --> 00:03:54,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Set an example.</font>

54
00:03:55,910 --> 00:03:57,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Serizawa-sensei.</font>

55
00:03:59,110 --> 00:04:02,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're so glad we joined you
 in the Miburo, sir.</font>

56
00:04:02,720 --> 00:04:05,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It makes us feel like we're really living 
and getting things done.</font>

57
00:04:05,920 --> 00:04:08,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That feeling counts for a lot.</font>

58
00:04:08,620 --> 00:04:09,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Next.</font>

59
00:04:10,170 --> 00:04:13,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I never thought the day would come 
when I'd wear two swords!</font>

60
00:04:13,600 --> 00:04:16,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With the right spirit, 
anyone can become anything.</font>

61
00:04:16,970 --> 00:04:17,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Next.</font>

62
00:04:17,680 --> 00:04:20,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, I can't believe you set up 
such a great party for us.</font>

63
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:22,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We had you all wrong.</font>

64
00:04:22,800 --> 00:04:26,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. We had you pegged 
as a rough-and-tumble tyrant.</font>

65
00:04:29,660 --> 00:04:31,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Never mind. Anything goes here.</font>

66
00:04:32,380 --> 00:04:33,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Next.</font>

67
00:04:33,650 --> 00:04:35,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can send money home 
to my ma in the country!</font>

68
00:04:35,910 --> 00:04:37,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can feel proud of myself!</font>

69
00:04:37,320 --> 00:04:40,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah? Glad to hear it. Next.</font>

70
00:04:40,760 --> 00:04:43,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Serizawa-sensei, let me say a few words!</font>

71
00:04:43,500 --> 00:04:44,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And me!</font>

72
00:04:44,640 --> 00:04:45,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sensei!</font>

73
00:04:45,630 --> 00:04:47,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come one, come all!</font>

74
00:04:59,630 --> 00:05:01,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are we really going through with it?</font>

75
00:05:05,080 --> 00:05:10,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we wait to ambush Serizawa's litter
 in all this wind and rain,</font>

76
00:05:11,120 --> 00:05:13,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">can we be sure we won't miss it?</font>

77
00:05:13,270 --> 00:05:14,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can.</font>

78
00:05:15,280 --> 00:05:18,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is killing Serizawa really 
the right thing to do?</font>

79
00:05:20,060 --> 00:05:23,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, I'll kill him 
if you tell me to, of course.</font>

80
00:05:23,970 --> 00:05:25,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I just...</font>

81
00:05:29,490 --> 00:05:33,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't help thinking it'd be a shame.</font>

82
00:05:33,260 --> 00:05:35,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Heisuke, back out of the plan.</font>

83
00:05:35,300 --> 00:05:36,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I—</font>

84
00:05:36,290 --> 00:05:37,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Back out!</font>

85
00:05:46,360 --> 00:05:47,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What now, genius?</font>

86
00:05:48,240 --> 00:05:49,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're down one guy.</font>

87
00:05:51,880 --> 00:05:53,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know you were thinking of Heisuke.</font>

88
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:57,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still, this will make the attack 
considerably more difficult.</font>

89
00:05:58,880 --> 00:06:01,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't want to take anyone
 who will have regrets.</font>

90
00:06:02,450 --> 00:06:04,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'll come back to bite us.</font>

91
00:06:10,930 --> 00:06:13,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It poured like this that day, too.</font>

92
00:06:14,640 --> 00:06:15,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Back when I was a kid.</font>

93
00:06:23,080 --> 00:06:25,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I spotted a kitten swept away
 by the river current.</font>

94
00:06:26,240 --> 00:06:29,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My older sister, who was with me,
dropped her umbrella and ran after it.</font>

95
00:06:30,240 --> 00:06:33,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The current was swift. Anyone could see
 she'd never save the kitten.</font>

96
00:06:34,040 --> 00:06:35,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told her...</font>

97
00:06:35,730 --> 00:06:38,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's hopeless. It's gonna die anyway.</font>

98
00:06:38,030 --> 00:06:39,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So what?</font>

99
00:06:45,140 --> 00:06:50,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The way she answered without hesitation
 struck me as beautiful.</font>

100
00:06:51,470 --> 00:06:52,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I learned then...</font>

101
00:06:53,810 --> 00:06:57,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that just because a storm is raging 
and something seems pointless,</font>

102
00:06:58,040 --> 00:07:00,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that's no excuse not to try.</font>

103
00:07:09,160 --> 00:07:13,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can't let it become known that 
we're acting on orders from Aizu.</font>

104
00:07:14,030 --> 00:07:17,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If word gets out, 
Aizu will withdraw support,</font>

105
00:07:17,000 --> 00:07:19,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and we'll lose our Shogunate backing.</font>

106
00:07:20,180 --> 00:07:22,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With the thread of our great cause cut,</font>

107
00:07:22,360 --> 00:07:26,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we'll go back to being the gaggle of ronin 
we started as. Just a gang of ruffians.</font>

108
00:07:27,760 --> 00:07:30,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If that happens, the Miburo is finished.</font>

109
00:07:32,080 --> 00:07:36,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So we need to prove the Miburo 
had no hand in what we're about to do.</font>

110
00:07:37,190 --> 00:07:39,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We need to come through
without a scratch on us.</font>

111
00:07:40,020 --> 00:07:44,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if that fails, we'll say 
the four of us acted alone,</font>

112
00:07:45,360 --> 00:07:48,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and that none of our comrades 
knew about our plan.</font>

113
00:07:48,600 --> 00:07:50,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, that part is true.</font>

114
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:52,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry.</font>

115
00:07:53,150 --> 00:07:56,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Miburo can rise again as long 
as we have Kondo-san to rally around.</font>

116
00:07:59,760 --> 00:08:03,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we fail tonight, 
we'll slit our bellies there and then.</font>

117
00:08:03,970 --> 00:08:07,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we take responsibility immediately,</font>

118
00:08:08,120 --> 00:08:10,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the rest of the Miburo can avoid blame.</font>

119
00:08:15,250 --> 00:08:17,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll do it. Alone, if I have to.</font>

120
00:08:19,080 --> 00:08:21,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't come with me unless 
you're prepared for the worst.</font>

121
00:08:22,240 --> 00:08:23,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't want to force you.</font>

122
00:08:25,790 --> 00:08:27,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't say my feelings have changed.</font>

123
00:08:27,950 --> 00:08:30,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like we're the Hijikata-gumi now.</font>

124
00:08:35,240 --> 00:08:38,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">From here on, we walk the path of Asura.</font>

125
00:08:42,850 --> 00:08:43,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm leaving.</font>

126
00:08:44,550 --> 00:08:46,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You there. Call a litter.</font>

127
00:08:46,880 --> 00:08:48,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir. At once.</font>

128
00:08:49,760 --> 00:08:51,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoops.</font>

129
00:08:52,780 --> 00:08:55,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rest easy. I already 
have a litter waiting.</font>

130
00:08:57,770 --> 00:08:59,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take this gentleman to Mibu.</font>

131
00:08:59,100 --> 00:08:59,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir.</font>

132
00:09:06,130 --> 00:09:07,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you thinking?</font>

133
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:10,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't dance to your tune.</font>

134
00:09:13,270 --> 00:09:16,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't like the look of these bearers.
I'll catch another litter.</font>

135
00:09:16,910 --> 00:09:18,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir! I'll hunt one down!</font>

136
00:09:18,640 --> 00:09:23,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll go back to Mibu for another round.
We've got women waiting for us.</font>

137
00:09:23,070 --> 00:09:24,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's our Sensei.</font>

138
00:09:24,620 --> 00:09:27,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No man in Kyoto can wow 
the ladies like you can.</font>

139
00:09:29,490 --> 00:09:31,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, what do we do now?</font>

140
00:09:31,010 --> 00:09:33,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The whole plan just swerved off-course.</font>

141
00:09:33,290 --> 00:09:34,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is a dilemma.</font>

142
00:09:34,970 --> 00:09:39,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can't have their litters left 
in the fields before we strike now.</font>

143
00:09:42,290 --> 00:09:44,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait till half past the fourth watch.</font>

144
00:09:44,280 --> 00:09:45,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

145
00:09:47,590 --> 00:09:52,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They'll disappear tonight. 
We'll make sure of that.</font>

146
00:10:04,440 --> 00:10:06,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, where are you going?</font>

147
00:10:07,360 --> 00:10:08,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For a piss.</font>

148
00:10:21,580 --> 00:10:23,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Three litters?</font>

149
00:10:23,000 --> 00:10:24,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who for? Serizawa-sensei 
and his buddies?</font>

150
00:10:29,190 --> 00:10:29,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nio!</font>

151
00:10:30,950 --> 00:10:33,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They're heading for Mibu. 
It really must be them.</i></font>

152
00:10:36,460 --> 00:10:38,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wh-What should I do?</i></font>

153
00:10:46,940 --> 00:10:49,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That lead litter looks heavier 
than the others.</i></font>

154
00:10:49,930 --> 00:10:52,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Serizawa-san must be in it.</i></font>

155
00:11:02,150 --> 00:11:06,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This road leads to the Yagis' house. 
They don't plan to stop on the way.</i></font>

156
00:11:09,320 --> 00:11:11,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's strange. 
I don't see any assassins.</i></font>

157
00:11:13,070 --> 00:11:17,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In fact, none of the other Miburo
 have even left Shimabara.</i></font>

158
00:11:17,370 --> 00:11:19,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So how can they waylay 
Serizawa-san's group?</i></font>

159
00:11:20,550 --> 00:11:24,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is today not the day? Was I wrong
 to think something would happen?</i></font>

160
00:11:25,720 --> 00:11:27,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'd better turn back for now and—</i></font>

161
00:11:35,800 --> 00:11:36,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There they are.</i></font>

162
00:11:37,720 --> 00:11:39,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I knew it.</i></font>

163
00:11:40,020 --> 00:11:40,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hijikata-san.</i></font>

164
00:11:41,160 --> 00:11:41,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Okita-san.</i></font>

165
00:11:42,480 --> 00:11:43,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Harada-san.</i></font>

166
00:11:43,790 --> 00:11:44,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Kondo-san?</i></font>

167
00:11:45,160 --> 00:11:46,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No.</i></font>

168
00:11:49,310 --> 00:11:50,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yamanami-san?</i></font>

169
00:11:51,510 --> 00:11:53,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Kondo-san isn't with them? Why not?</i></font>

170
00:11:55,110 --> 00:11:57,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Was he never one of 
the assassins to begin with?</i></font>

171
00:12:03,120 --> 00:12:06,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Serizawa-sensei and his buddies 
really were in those litters.</i></font>

172
00:12:12,060 --> 00:12:13,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've got a bad feeling about this.</i></font>

173
00:12:13,620 --> 00:12:16,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Something's coming. 
Something terrible's about to—</i></font>

174
00:12:23,080 --> 00:12:25,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Nio? Why's he going back?</i></font>

175
00:12:25,600 --> 00:12:27,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't get it.</i></font>

176
00:12:27,220 --> 00:12:28,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aw, who gives a crap?</font>

177
00:12:29,170 --> 00:12:32,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've got bigger problems.
I need to get to Serizawa-sensei fast.</font>

178
00:12:49,640 --> 00:12:50,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who's that?</font>

179
00:12:50,960 --> 00:12:52,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like a kid.</font>

180
00:12:57,210 --> 00:12:59,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hm? What's up? Oh, Nio! It's you.</font>

181
00:13:00,460 --> 00:13:03,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey now. You know kids 
aren't allowed in here.</font>

182
00:13:03,200 --> 00:13:03,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Make way.</font>

183
00:13:05,200 --> 00:13:05,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nope.</font>

184
00:13:05,960 --> 00:13:07,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aw, forget it.</font>

185
00:13:07,400 --> 00:13:08,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nio.</font>

186
00:13:12,680 --> 00:13:15,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing here?</font>

187
00:13:17,800 --> 00:13:19,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kondo-san.</font>

188
00:13:22,280 --> 00:13:23,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you mean?</font>

189
00:13:23,660 --> 00:13:25,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm talking about Serizawa-san.</font>

190
00:13:25,670 --> 00:13:27,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As commander, 
you must know what's happening.</font>

191
00:13:27,950 --> 00:13:29,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not another word.</font>

192
00:13:36,920 --> 00:13:40,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm angry, you know.</font>

193
00:13:45,730 --> 00:13:47,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, what's up?</font>

194
00:13:47,220 --> 00:13:48,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is there trouble?</font>

195
00:13:49,480 --> 00:13:52,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, gentlemen! 
I'm about to tell you all a tale.</font>

196
00:13:53,780 --> 00:13:56,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ten years had passed 
since the Black Ships came.</font>

197
00:13:56,660 --> 00:13:58,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Through our millennium-old capital, Kyoto,</font>

198
00:13:58,980 --> 00:14:02,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">rogues swaggered, 
law and order a thing of the past.</font>

199
00:14:03,090 --> 00:14:06,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Shogunate put out a call in Edo 
to do something about it.</font>

200
00:14:07,340 --> 00:14:11,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And 234 samurai rose to the challenge.</font>

201
00:14:11,930 --> 00:14:13,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, something's starting up.</font>

202
00:14:13,670 --> 00:14:14,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Entertainment?</font>

203
00:14:14,760 --> 00:14:15,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's hear it.</font>

204
00:14:15,830 --> 00:14:19,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yet they were all ruffians, 
confident in their skill with a blade.</font>

205
00:14:19,650 --> 00:14:22,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Their journey to Kyoto 
could not pass without incident.</font>

206
00:14:23,740 --> 00:14:26,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hear what we Miburo faced on the road.</font>

207
00:14:26,020 --> 00:14:28,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's sure to leave you 
on the floor laughing.</font>

208
00:14:28,330 --> 00:14:30,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, listen up!</font>

209
00:14:30,370 --> 00:14:31,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, a story?</font>

210
00:14:31,940 --> 00:14:33,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Great! Start telling it!</font>

211
00:14:34,470 --> 00:14:36,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Angry, you say?</font>

212
00:14:42,340 --> 00:14:45,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Be calm. Be calm.</font>

213
00:14:51,860 --> 00:14:54,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why did you allow something like this?</font>

214
00:14:55,280 --> 00:15:00,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why did you send your allies to do it 
without taking part yourself?</font>

215
00:15:01,160 --> 00:15:03,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It goes against the sincerity
 we made our emblem.</font>

216
00:15:03,520 --> 00:15:06,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But more than that, Kondo-san, 
it doesn't seem like <i>you</i>.</font>

217
00:15:11,780 --> 00:15:14,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because Serizawa-san has strayed 
from the path of humanity.</font>

218
00:15:15,200 --> 00:15:18,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The path of humanity? 
What do you mean by that?</font>

219
00:15:27,320 --> 00:15:28,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Serizawa-san...</font>

220
00:15:30,680 --> 00:15:32,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">seems to be suffering from an illness.</font>

221
00:15:34,650 --> 00:15:36,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He hasn't had a doctor examine him,</font>

222
00:15:37,750 --> 00:15:40,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but he said he can feel it 
spreading through his body.</font>

223
00:15:41,960 --> 00:15:44,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are times he can 
barely hold his sword.</font>

224
00:15:45,470 --> 00:15:47,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He said he's running out of time.</font>

225
00:15:49,080 --> 00:15:51,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kondo Isami was charged 
to arrange lodgings,</font>

226
00:15:51,960 --> 00:15:55,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but somehow, he forgot to book 
a room for Serizawa Kamo.</font>

227
00:15:56,190 --> 00:15:59,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Serizawa raged. 
Kondo could only apologize.</font>

228
00:15:59,480 --> 00:16:01,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They stared each other down
 amid the flames.</font>

229
00:16:01,830 --> 00:16:04,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, what could fate 
have in store for them?</font>

230
00:16:05,800 --> 00:16:07,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hurry up and tell us!</font>

231
00:16:07,860 --> 00:16:11,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I understand the position you 
and your allies are in. After all...</font>

232
00:16:11,420 --> 00:16:13,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do something about Serizawa.</font>

233
00:16:13,880 --> 00:16:15,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aizu takes this seriously.</font>

234
00:16:16,390 --> 00:16:17,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was at that meeting.</font>

235
00:16:19,890 --> 00:16:22,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But getting rid of Serizawa-san—</font>

236
00:16:21,780 --> 00:16:22,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Nio.</font>

237
00:16:22,790 --> 00:16:24,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not another word.</font>

238
00:16:28,000 --> 00:16:30,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't brush me off 
just because I'm a child.</font>

239
00:16:30,860 --> 00:16:32,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't hold it in anymore.</font>

240
00:16:32,660 --> 00:16:34,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I insist you hear me out.</font>

241
00:16:35,480 --> 00:16:36,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tell me, then.</font>

242
00:16:37,140 --> 00:16:39,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why didn't you take action
 as an inspector?</font>

243
00:16:39,990 --> 00:16:43,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You could made this affair public
 if you had the mind to.</font>

244
00:16:45,150 --> 00:16:46,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How can I possibly tell anyone?</font>

245
00:16:47,600 --> 00:16:50,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even I have enough sense to see that.</font>

246
00:16:51,420 --> 00:16:53,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"The path of humanity." I see.</font>

247
00:16:56,450 --> 00:16:57,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mean Okiku-chan's fate.</font>

248
00:16:59,670 --> 00:17:02,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But that wasn't Serizawa-san's fault.</font>

249
00:17:03,380 --> 00:17:04,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You asked him?</font>

250
00:17:04,350 --> 00:17:05,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I did.</font>

251
00:17:05,680 --> 00:17:08,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But he wouldn't tell me 
any more than that.</font>

252
00:17:09,070 --> 00:17:11,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't believe Serizawa-san killed her.</font>

253
00:17:12,100 --> 00:17:13,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It isn't in his nature.</font>

254
00:17:14,000 --> 00:17:14,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then—</font>

255
00:17:14,840 --> 00:17:17,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But he did know something.</font>

256
00:17:17,070 --> 00:17:21,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In which case, should he not have 
told the truth, at least to the Yagis?</font>

257
00:17:22,040 --> 00:17:24,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That is why I waited a month.</font>

258
00:17:25,280 --> 00:17:27,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why couldn't he tell them?</font>

259
00:17:27,500 --> 00:17:28,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He was frightened.</font>

260
00:17:29,080 --> 00:17:31,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He surely held his tongue 
to put his own safety first.</font>

261
00:17:32,710 --> 00:17:35,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He acted so unlike 
the Serizawa-san I know.</font>

262
00:17:37,640 --> 00:17:41,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not everyone can be as strong
 as you are, Kondo-san.</font>

263
00:17:41,960 --> 00:17:43,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">People get scared sometimes.</font>

264
00:17:46,800 --> 00:17:49,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I placed this matter in Toshi's hands.</font>

265
00:17:49,230 --> 00:17:52,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't interfere. I promised him that.</font>

266
00:17:53,510 --> 00:17:55,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I did it to preserve the Miburo.</font>

267
00:17:55,560 --> 00:17:58,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't want to hear something like that.</font>

268
00:17:58,130 --> 00:17:59,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe it's because I'm a kid,</font>

269
00:18:00,080 --> 00:18:02,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but it doesn't resonate with me.</font>

270
00:18:02,140 --> 00:18:02,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that...</font>

271
00:18:03,530 --> 00:18:07,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">because deep down, 
it doesn't satisfy you, either?</font>

272
00:18:08,230 --> 00:18:10,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My own wishes are beside the point.</font>

273
00:18:10,150 --> 00:18:12,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then what about Serizawa-san's wishes?</font>

274
00:18:13,210 --> 00:18:14,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He told me...</font>

275
00:18:16,120 --> 00:18:18,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The measure of a samurai is his death.</font>

276
00:18:19,280 --> 00:18:22,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have nothing more left to do.</font>

277
00:18:22,650 --> 00:18:25,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if I possibly can...</font>

278
00:18:33,120 --> 00:18:37,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"I want to face Sir Kondo
 in a final duel."</font>

279
00:18:39,200 --> 00:18:41,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This won't end unless you go to him.</font>

280
00:18:41,740 --> 00:18:44,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will you take even that wish
 from Serizawa-san?</font>

281
00:18:45,630 --> 00:18:47,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Leaving him to your allies?</font>

282
00:18:50,650 --> 00:18:52,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pretending you had 
nothing to do with it?</font>

283
00:18:53,740 --> 00:18:55,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Niimi-san is gone now, too.</font>

284
00:18:55,860 --> 00:19:00,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once Serizawa-san dies, 
you'll lead the Miburo, won't you?</font>

285
00:19:00,040 --> 00:19:02,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No. I lack what it takes.</font>

286
00:19:02,800 --> 00:19:03,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You will anyway!</font>

287
00:19:05,780 --> 00:19:10,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone will follow you because 
you're truly strong in body and mind.</font>

288
00:19:10,380 --> 00:19:13,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know they will. I think I will, too.</font>

289
00:19:13,990 --> 00:19:17,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Deep down, everyone wants to be strong.</font>

290
00:19:17,150 --> 00:19:20,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To be diligent, earnest, and righteous.</font>

291
00:19:21,150 --> 00:19:23,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looking at some, you wouldn't think it.</font>

292
00:19:24,660 --> 00:19:26,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's all right to let loose
 once in a while.</font>

293
00:19:27,380 --> 00:19:29,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You shouldn't need me to tell you that.</font>

294
00:19:29,910 --> 00:19:31,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because we're weak.</font>

295
00:19:31,800 --> 00:19:34,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We want to slack off.
To take the easy way out.</font>

296
00:19:34,920 --> 00:19:35,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

297
00:19:38,870 --> 00:19:46,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<b><font face="Georgia"><font size="40"><font color="#ffffff"><font color="#b3d8ee">Sincerity</font></font></font></font></b></font>

298
00:19:39,560 --> 00:19:43,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't forgiving that weakness, 
and reaching out to it,</font>

299
00:19:43,700 --> 00:19:45,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">what sincerity is all about?</font>

300
00:19:46,520 --> 00:19:50,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What good is a commander who 
can't even grant a comrade's request?</font>

301
00:19:51,550 --> 00:19:56,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're about to step off the 
"path of humanity" as we speak.</font>

302
00:19:59,010 --> 00:20:01,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you're going to bear 
the burden of the Miburo,</font>

303
00:20:02,080 --> 00:20:03,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">bear <i>all</i> of it.</font>

304
00:20:09,480 --> 00:20:12,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forgive me for speaking 
so insolently.</font>

305
00:20:14,320 --> 00:20:16,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Listen, Sir Kondo.</font>

306
00:20:16,200 --> 00:20:18,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What tomorrow holds for the Miburo is...</font>

307
00:20:21,200 --> 00:20:23,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My dear ronin of Mibu!</font>

308
00:20:27,010 --> 00:20:28,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong, Sir Kondo?</font>

309
00:20:29,110 --> 00:20:31,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A leader's got to cut a fine figure.</font>

310
00:20:31,700 --> 00:20:33,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Set an example.</font>

311
00:20:35,270 --> 00:20:35,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nio.</font>

312
00:20:36,620 --> 00:20:38,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you have an evening star?</font>

313
00:20:41,160 --> 00:20:42,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean a north star.</font>

314
00:20:43,780 --> 00:20:46,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm told all sailors navigate by it.</font>

315
00:20:48,700 --> 00:20:50,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It never wavers.</font>

316
00:20:50,450 --> 00:20:54,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">While they can see it, 
they will never lose their way.</font>

317
00:20:55,000 --> 00:20:57,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He has been my guiding compass.</font>

318
00:20:58,640 --> 00:21:01,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In fact, he stands above
 all other samurai.</font>

319
00:21:07,400 --> 00:21:08,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let us go.</font>

320
00:21:09,090 --> 00:21:10,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kondo-san.</font>

321
00:21:12,040 --> 00:21:15,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look at you, Kondo-sensei! 
You're falling down drunk!</font>

322
00:21:15,040 --> 00:21:16,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You shouldn't have had so much.</font>

323
00:21:16,790 --> 00:21:18,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nio, lead him to the outhouse.</font>

324
00:21:19,370 --> 00:21:20,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes, sir.</font>

325
00:21:20,800 --> 00:21:22,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll handle things here.</font>

326
00:21:22,460 --> 00:21:23,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Todo-san.</font>

327
00:21:23,390 --> 00:21:24,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go on.</font>

328
00:21:24,650 --> 00:21:25,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We must hurry.</font>

329
00:21:25,870 --> 00:21:26,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir.</font>

330
00:21:27,260 --> 00:21:32,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><b><font size="40">The Path of Asura</font></b></font></font>

331
00:21:38,220 --> 00:21:40,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-Who's there?</font>

332
00:23:20,040 --> 00:23:25,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="TImes New Roman"><font size="26"><b>{\an8}Next time</b></font></font></font>

333
00:23:20,470 --> 00:23:21,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's me, Harada Sanosuke.</font>

334
00:23:22,340 --> 00:23:26,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Serizawa, I won't let you off the hook 
for what you did to Hasumukai.</font>

335
00:23:27,180 --> 00:23:32,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stabbing you in the dark isn't my style,
 but Soji's got a point.</font>

336
00:23:32,170 --> 00:23:34,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We gotta go with 
whatever works at this point.</font>

337
00:23:34,410 --> 00:23:39,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll show you what I can do when 
I've got a spear in my hands.</font>

338
00:23:39,520 --> 00:23:42,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Hang on. Something seems off.</font>

